Description: Open-source AI-engineering analytics collector.
 Bema captures LLM/coding-agent usage from local developer machines
 (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, Continue, Copilot, Cline/Roo/Kilo) and ships
 it to a tenant-owned backend for cost, outcome, and efficiency analysis.
 This package installs the single-binary `bematist` collector.
